    const MESSAGE_24 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EDaisy\r\n\x81@On Peony\r\n\x81@Using Light Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nCan anyone catch her when\r\nshe uses her Shining Wing\r\nspell?\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ECosmos\r\n\x81@On Peony\r\n\x81@Using Darkness Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nCosmos, Daisy's twin sister,\r\nhas magic opposite but\r\nalmost as powerful in her\r\nDark Wing spell.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nseventh match will be the\r\nday after tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_25 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EAmaryllis\r\n\x81@On Sakuya\r\n\x81@Using Flower Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAll her magic does is create\r\nflowers, which really isn't\r\nthat useful in racing...\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELiliac\r\n\x81@On Karin\r\n\x81@Trainee in Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAs a trainee, Lilac has no\r\nmagic yet. Let's hope she\r\neventually makes good.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nseventh match will be\r\ntomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_26 = "The results of the seventh\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nEverybody's favorite racer,\r\nDaisy, is back at last! And\r\nas expected, she and Cosmos\r\nled the way right from the\r\nstart with their combination\r\nmagic. And from the looks of\r\nthings, it seems fair to say\r\nthat Daisy is completely\r\nrecovered from her accident.\r\nA fierce battle for third\r\nplace broke out between\r\nSylvia and Miltonia, which\r\nended in the final lap, when\r\nMiltonia, having exhausted\r\nher magic power, was\r\nhelpless to stop Sylvia from\r\nusing her wind magic to pass\r\nher by.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Daisy\r\n2nd Place: Cosmos\r\n3rd Place: Sylvia\x05"
    const MESSAGE_27 = "The results of the seventh\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Daisy  +10\r\n2nd Place: Cosmos  +6\r\n3rd Place: Sylvia  +4\r\n4th Place: Miltonia  +3\r\n5th Place: Moraea  +2\r\n6th Place: Leatrice  +1\r\n7th Place: Lavender\r\n8th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (unch.): Sylvia   38\r\n2nd (up): Miltonia  35\r\n3rd (down): Lupinus  34\r\n4th (unch.): Daisy  32\r\n5th (down): Cosmos  28\r\n6th (unch.): Moraea  8\r\n7th (down): Amaryllis  6\r\n8th (up): Leatrice  1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_28 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMoraea\r\n\x81@On Natsuki\r\n\x81@Using Summoning Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nI've never seen her summon\r\nanything, though, so I don't\r\nrightly know just what this\r\nmeans.\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELupinus\r\n\x81@On Misuzu\r\n\x81@Using Illusion Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAll she does is illusion, so\r\nif you figure that out,\r\nshe's totally powerless.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\neighth match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_29 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ESylvia\r\n\x81@On Yotsuba\r\n\x81@Using Spirit Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nSylvia's new machine,\r\nYotsuba, can apparently\r\nchange into any of four\r\ndifferent forms, in\r\naccordance with whichever\r\nmagic she is using at a\r\ngiven time. We'll just have\r\nto see what this is all\r\nabout.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMiltonia\r\n\x81@On Sprite\r\n\x81@Using White Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe uses restorative magic,\r\nso she prefers to race\r\npretty hard, and then heal\r\nherself afterwards.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\neighth match will be\r\ntomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_30 = "The results of the eighth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLupinus, who was first in\r\nthe qualifying round, made\r\neffective use of her mirror\r\nimage and other magics to\r\nkeep anyone else from\r\ngetting past her, holding on\r\nto the lead all the way to\r\nthe final lap. As a result,\r\nshe also took top place in\r\nthe overall standings away\r\nfrom Sylvia. Speaking of\r\nwhom, she staked the race on\r\nher new machine, Yotsuba.\r\nDue to it not being properly\r\ntuned yet, however, she only\r\ncame in sixth. Oh, and while\r\nit isn't that big a deal, we\r\nfeel we should mention that\r\nLavender earned her first\r\npoints ever, as per her\r\ndivination prior to the\r\nstart of the race.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Lupinus\r\n2nd Place: Daisy\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos\x05"
    const MESSAGE_31 = "The results of the eighth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Lupinus  +10\r\n2nd Place: Daisy  +6\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos  +4\r\n4th Place: Lavender  +3\r\n5th Place: Miltonia  +2\r\n6th Place: Sylvia  +1\r\n7th Place: Leatrice\r\n8th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (up): Lupinus  44\r\n2nd (down): Sylvia  39\r\n3rd (up): Daisy  39\r\n4th (down): Miltonia  37\r\n5th (unch.): Cosmos  32\r\n6th (unch.): Moraea  8\r\n7th (unch.): Amaryllis  6\r\n8th (up): Lavender  3\r\n9th (down): Leatrice  1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_32 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nare as follows:\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELeatrice\r\n\x81@On Sana\r\n\x81@Using Voodoo\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe can always be seen\r\ngoing around before the race\r\nwith dolls and needles. She\r\ndoesn't do much at all\r\nduring the race proper.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELavender\r\n\x81@On Starlight\r\n\x81@Using Divination\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe always divines who will\r\nwin before a race starts.\r\nRumor has it her predictions\r\nare 100% accurate.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nninth match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_33 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EDaisy\r\n\x81@On Peony\r\n\x81@Using Light Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nCan anyone catch her when\r\nshe uses her Shining Wing\r\nspell?\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ECosmos\r\n\x81@On Peony\r\n\x81@Using Darkness Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nCosmos, Daisy's twin sister,\r\nhas magic opposite but\r\nalmost as powerful in her\r\nDark Wing spell.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nninth match will be\r\ntomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_34 = "The results of the ninth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThe weather was bad for\r\ntoday's race, meaning that\r\nit was raining so hard\r\nduring the race that you\r\ncouldn't see anything beyond\r\na few meters. So, while\r\neveryone else took it slow\r\nand easy, Miltonia charged\r\nahead, unconcerned about\r\ngetting hurt, thanks to\r\nliberal use of her\r\nrestorative magics. In this\r\nreckless manner, she managed\r\nto take first place, though\r\nshe also ended up overdoing\r\nit in the process, hurting\r\nherself pretty badly. It\r\nnow looks as though she\r\nwon't make it to the final\r\nrace, which is a real shame,\r\nseeing as how she finally\r\ntook top place in the\r\noverall standings, too.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Miltonia\r\n2nd Place: Daisy\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos\x05"
    const MESSAGE_35 = "The results of the ninth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Miltonia  +10\r\n2nd Place: Daisy  +6\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos  +4\r\n4th Place: Sylvia  +3\r\n5th Place: Lupinus  +2\r\n6th Place: Amaryllis  +1\r\n7th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (up): Miltonia  47\r\n2nd (down): Lupinus 46\r\n3rd (unch.): Daisy  44\r\n4th (down): Sylvia  42\r\n5th (unch.): Cosmos  36\r\n6th (unch.): Moraea  8\r\n7th (unch.): Amaryllis  7\r\n8th (unch.): Lavender  3\r\n9th: Leatrice: 1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_36 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EAmaryllis\r\n\x81@On Sakuya\r\n\x81@Using Flower Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAll her magic does is create\r\nflowers, which really isn't\r\nthat useful in racing...\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELiliac\r\n\x81@On Karin\r\n\x81@Trainee in Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAs a trainee, Lilac has no\r\nmagic yet. Let's hope she\r\neventually makes good.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nfinal match will be the\r\nday after tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_37 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMoraea\r\n\x81@On Natsuki\r\n\x81@Using Summoning Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nI've never seen her summon\r\nanything, though, so I don't\r\nrightly know just what this\r\nmeans.\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELupinus\r\n\x81@On Misuzu\r\n\x81@Using Illusion Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAll she does is illusion, so\r\nif you figure that out,\r\nshe's totally powerless.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nfinal match will be\r\ntomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_38 = "The results of the final\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nSadly, Miltonia had to be\r\nscratched, and thus, the\r\nchampionship came down to\r\nthe top three point holders.\r\nYotsuba, Sylvia's new\r\nmachine, finally showed us\r\nwhat it can do. This machine\r\nhas four modes that are\r\ncapable of handling any\r\nterrain, including a wind\r\nmode that not even the\r\ncombination magic used by\r\nDaisy and Cosmos could beat.\r\nThis victory put Sylvia back\r\non top in total points. Our\r\ncongratulations to her.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Sylvia\r\n2nd Place: Daisy\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos\x05"
    const MESSAGE_39 = "The results of the final\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Sylvia  +10\r\n2nd Place: Daisy  +6\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos  +4\r\n4th Place: Lupinus  +3\r\n5th Place: Lavender  +2\r\n6th Place: Moraea  +1\r\n7th Place: Amaryllis\r\n8th Place: Leatrice\r\n9th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (up): Sylvia  52\r\n2nd (up): Daisy  50\r\n3rd (down): Lupinus  49\r\n4th (down): Miltonia  47\r\n5th (unch.): Cosmos  40\r\n6th (unch.): Moraea  9\r\n7th (unch.): Amaryllis  7\r\n8th (unch.): Lavender  5\r\n9th (unch.): Leatrice  1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_40 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ESylvia\r\n\x81@On Yotsuba\r\n\x81@Using Spirit Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nSylvia's new machine,\r\nYotsuba, can apparently\r\nchange into any of four\r\ndifferent forms, in\r\naccordance with whichever\r\nmagic she is using at a\r\ngiven time. We'll just have\r\nto see what this is all\r\nabout.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMiltonia\r\n\x81@On Sprite\r\n\x81@Using White Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe uses restorative magic,\r\nso she prefers to race\r\npretty hard, and then heal\r\nherself afterwards.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nfirst match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_41 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELicorice\r\n\x81@On Makoto\r\n\x81@Using Spatial Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLicorice's spatial\r\ninterchange magic, which\r\nenables her to change places\r\nwith anyone else, may well\r\nbe the most powerful magic\r\nof all.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELavender\r\n\x81@On Starlight\r\n\x81@Using Divination\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe always divines who will\r\nwin before a race starts.\r\nRumor has it her predictions\r\nare 100% accurate.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nfirst match will be\r\ntomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_42 = "The results of the first\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nIn her first race ever,\r\nLicorice came in first. What\r\nhappened was that in the\r\nfinal lap, she sneakily used\r\nher spatial interchange\r\nmagic to switch places with\r\nSylvia, who had been in the\r\nlead up to that point. There\r\nare calls now, however, for\r\nthis type of magic to be\x82\xCD\r\nbanned as too dangerous for\r\nuse in certain spellcasting\r\nsituations. Further\r\ninformation will be reported\r\nas it becomes available.\r\nSylvia ended up dead last,\r\nby the way.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice\r\n2nd Place: Daisy\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos\x05"
    const MESSAGE_43 = "The results of the first\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st: Licorice  +10\r\n2nd: Daisy  +6\r\n3rd: Cosmos  +4\r\n4th: Lupinus  +3\r\n5th: Miltonia  +2\r\n6th: Moraea  +1\r\n7th: Amaryllis\r\n8th: Lavender\r\n9th: Lilac\r\n10th: Sylvia\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st: Licorice  10\r\n2nd: Daisy  6\r\n3rd: Cosmos  4\r\n4th: Lupinus  3\r\n5th: Miltonia  2\r\n6th: Moraea  1\r\n\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_44 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EDaisy\r\n\x81@On Peony\r\n\x81@Using Light Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nCan anyone catch her when\r\nshe uses her Shining Wing\r\nspell?\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ECosmos\r\n\x81@On Peony\r\n\x81@Using Darkness Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nCosmos, Daisy's twin sister,\r\nhas magic opposite but\r\nalmost as powerful in her\r\nDark Wing spell.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nsecond match will be the\r\nday after tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_45 = "The results of the second\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLicorice, who had just won\r\nher first race, is on the\r\ninjured list. It seems that\r\nher spatial interchange\r\nmagic burns a fair amount of\r\nmagic power, and thus, can't\r\nbe used all that often. As\r\nfor Sylvia, she was still\r\napparently pretty burned by\r\nhaving ended up dead last in\r\nthe previous race, and just\r\ndidn't run a very good race\r\nat all this time around. In\r\nthe event, this race came\r\ndown to Daisy and Cosmos on\r\nthe one hand, and Lupinus on\r\nthe other. By skillfully\r\ninterposing her mirror\r\nimages between Daisy and\r\nCosmos, Lupinus was able to\r\nkeep them from using their\r\ncombination magic, and thus\r\nwin the race.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Lupinus\r\n2nd Place: Daisy\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos\x05"
    const MESSAGE_46 = "The results of the second\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Lupinus  +10\r\n2nd Place: Daisy  +6\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos  +4\r\n4th Place: Miltonia  +3\r\n5th Place: Moraea  +2\r\n6th Place: Amaryllis  +1\r\n7th Place: Sylvia\r\n8th Place: Lavender\r\n9th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (up): Lupinus  13\r\n2nd (unch.): Daisy  12\r\n3rd (down): Licorice  10\r\n4th (down): Cosmos  8\r\n5th (unch.): Miltonia  5\r\n6th (unch.): Moraea  3\r\n7th (up): Amaryllis  1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_47 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMoraea\r\n\x81@On Natsuki\r\n\x81@Using Summoning Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nI've never seen her summon\r\nanything, though, so I don't\r\nrightly know just what this\r\nmeans.\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELupinus\r\n\x81@On Misuzu\r\n\x81@Using Illusion Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAll she does is illusion, so\r\nif you figure that out,\r\nshe's totally powerless.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nthird match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_48 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ESylvia\r\n\x81@On Yotsuba\r\n\x81@Using Spirit Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nSylvia's new machine,\r\nYotsuba, can apparently\r\nchange into any of four\r\ndifferent forms, in\r\naccordance with whichever\r\nmagic she is using at a\r\ngiven time. We'll just have\r\nto see what this is all\r\nabout.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMiltonia\r\n\x81@On Sprite\r\n\x81@Using White Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe uses restorative magic,\r\nso she prefers to race\r\npretty hard, and then heal\r\nherself afterwards.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nthird match will be\r\ntomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_49 = "The results of the third\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAs with the previous race,\r\nLicorice sat out this one\r\ntoo. The difference is that\r\nshe didn't enter this one,\r\nshe says, because she didn't\r\nvery much feel like it,\r\nadding that she would be in\r\nthe next one, however. It\r\nthus appeared that this race\r\nwould be down to Daisy and\r\nCosmos versus Lupinus again,\r\njust like the previous one,\r\nexcept that Miltonia also\r\njoined in this time, to make\r\nit a three-sided contest.\r\nThe outcome was decided when\r\nDaisy and Cosmos used a\r\nmomentary advantage to cast\r\ntheir combination magic,\r\nthus taking first and second\r\nplace, followed by Miltonia\r\nand Lupinus, in that order.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Daisy\r\n2nd Place: Cosmos\r\n3rd Place: Miltonia\x05"
    const MESSAGE_50 = "The results of the third\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Daisy  +10\r\n2nd Place: Cosmos  +6\r\n3rd Place: Miltonia  +4\r\n4th Place: Lupinus  +3\r\n5th Place: Amaryllis  +2\r\n6th Place: Moraea  +1\r\n7th Place: Lavender\r\n8th Place: Sylvia\r\n9th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (up): Daisy  22\r\n2nd (down): Lupinus  16\r\n3rd (up): Cosmos  14\r\n4th (down): Licorice  10\r\n5th (unch.): Miltonia  9\r\n6th (unch.): Moraea  4\r\n7th (up): Amaryllis  3\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_51 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELicorice\r\n\x81@On Makoto\r\n\x81@Using Spatial Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLicorice's spatial\r\ninterchange magic, which\r\nenables her to change places\r\nwith anyone else, may well\r\nbe the most powerful magic\r\nof all.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELavender\r\n\x81@On Starlight\r\n\x81@Using Divination\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe always divines who will\r\nwin before a race starts.\r\nRumor has it her predictions\r\nare 100% accurate.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nfourth match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_52 = "The results of the fourth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLicorice, who had been\r\non the injured list ever\r\nsince winning her very first\r\nrace ever, got back on the\r\ntrack for the first time\r\ntoday. Sylvia wasted no time\r\nin complaining to Licorice\r\nabout the magic that\r\nLicorice used in that first\r\nrace, however. People around\r\nthem stopped the conflict at\r\nthe time, but words don't\r\nappear to have been enough\r\nfor Sylvia, whose anger came\r\nout in a bad way during the\r\nrace, when she collided with\r\nLupinus, taking them both\r\nout of the running. Licorice\r\nwent on to win the race,\r\nwithout using her spatial\r\ninterchange magic.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice\r\n2nd Place: Daisy\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos\x05"
    const MESSAGE_53 = "The results of the fourth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice  +10\r\n2nd Place: Daisy  +6\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos  +4\r\n4th Place: Miltonia  +3\r\n5th Place: Moraea  +2\r\n6th Place: Lavender  +1\r\n7th Place: Amaryllis\r\n8th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (unch.): Daisy  28\r\n2nd (up): Licorice  20\r\n3rd (unch.): Cosmos  18\r\n4th (down): Lupinus  16\r\n5th (unch.): Miltonia  12\r\n6th (unch.): Moraea  6\r\n7th (unch.): Amaryllis  3\r\n8th (up)  Lavender  1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_54 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EAmaryllis\r\n\x81@On Sakuya\r\n\x81@Using Flower Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAll her magic does is create\r\nflowers, which really isn't\r\nthat useful in racing...\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELiliac\r\n\x81@On Karin\r\n\x81@Trainee in Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAs a trainee, Lilac has no\r\nmagic yet. Let's hope she\r\neventually makes good.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nfifth match will be the\r\nday after tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_55 = "The results of the fifth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThis time around, Lavender's\r\ndivination foretold that she\r\nand Daisy were going to\r\ncollide. Naturally, Daisy\r\nwasn't going to take news\r\nlike that lying down. She\r\ndid her level best to stay\r\naway from Lavender during\r\nthe race, only to suddenly\r\nfind herself being lapped.\r\nAnd wouldn't you know it?\r\nJust then, Lavender's\r\nmachine breaks down,\r\ndecelerates, and slides over\r\nto hit Daisy, who at this\r\npoint is behind her at an\r\nangle, taking them both out\r\nof the race. It appears\r\nthere really is no escape\r\nfrom Lavender's divinations,\r\nafter all. As a result of\r\nher crash, Daisy was passed\r\nup in the overall standings\r\nby Licorice.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice\r\n2nd Place: Cosmos\r\n3rd Place: Lupinus\x05"
    const MESSAGE_56 = "The results of the fifth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice  +10\r\n2nd Place: Cosmos  +6\r\n3rd Place: Lupinus  +4\r\n4th Place: Sylvia  +3\r\n5th Place: Miltonia  +2\r\n6th Place: Amaryllis  +1\r\n7th Place: Moraea\r\n8th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (up): Licorice  30\r\n2nd (down): Daisy  28\r\n3rd (unch.): Cosmos  24\r\n4th (unch.): Lupinus  20\r\n5th (unch.): Miltonia  14\r\n6th (unch.): Moraea  6\r\n7th (unch.): Amaryllis  4\r\n8th (up): Sylvia  3\r\n9th (down): Lavender  1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_57 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ESylvia\r\n\x81@On Yotsuba\r\n\x81@Using Spirit Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nSylvia's new machine,\r\nYotsuba, can change into any\r\nof four different forms, in\r\naccordance with whichever\r\nmagic she is using at a\r\ngiven time. It's a good one.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMiltonia\r\n\x81@On Sprite\r\n\x81@Using White Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe uses restorative magic,\r\nso she prefers to race\r\npretty hard, and then heal\r\nherself afterwards.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nsixth match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_58 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELicorice\r\n\x81@On Makoto\r\n\x81@Using Spatial Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLicorice's spatial\r\ninterchange magic, which\r\nenables her to change places\r\nwith anyone else, may well\r\nbe the most powerful magic\r\nof all.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELavender\r\n\x81@On Starlight\r\n\x81@Using Divination\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe always divines who will\r\nwin before a race starts.\r\nRumor has it her predictions\r\nare 100% accurate.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nsixth match will be\r\ntomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_59 = "The results of the sixth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThis time around, it was\r\nDaisy's turn to get nailed\r\nby Licorice's spatial\r\ninterchange magic. She ended\r\nup right smack behind\r\nAmaryllis and Moraea, and,\r\nunable to effectively dodge\r\neither of them, instead\r\nplowed into them both, thus\r\ntaking all three of them out\r\nof the race. Daisy thus fell\r\nto third place in the\r\noverall standings, being\r\npassed up in the process by\r\nher sister, Cosmos. The\x82\xCD\r\nquestion now is, having used\r\nher spatial interchange\r\nmagic, will Licorice sit out\r\nthe next race, as happened\r\nlast time?\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice\r\n2nd Place: Cosmos\r\n3rd Place: Lupinus\x05"
    const MESSAGE_60 = "The results of the sixth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice  +10\r\n2nd Place: Cosmos  +6\r\n3rd Place: Lupinus  +4\r\n4th Place: Sylvia  +3\r\n5th Place: Miltonia  +2\r\n6th Place: Lavender  +1\r\n7th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (unch.): Licorice  40\r\n2nd (up): Cosmos  30\r\n3rd (down): Daisy  28\r\n4th (unch.): Lupinus  24\r\n5th (unch.): Miltonia  16\r\n6th (unch.): Moraea  6\r\n6th (up): Sylvia  6\r\n8th (down): Amaryllis  4\r\n9th (unch.): Lavender  2\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_61 = "The results of the seventh\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nTo no one's surprise,\r\nLicorice did indeed sit out\r\nthis race Instead, the\r\nwinner of this race turned\r\nout to be Lupinus, on her\r\nbrand new machine, Maho. By\r\nskillfully blocking Daisy\r\nand Cosmos from using their\r\nmagic, she kept the field\r\nrunning at her own pace,\r\nfrom start to finish, taking\r\nthe win without a struggle.\r\nAs a result, Lupinus, Daisy,\r\nand Cosmos are now in a\r\nthree-way tie for second\r\nplace in the overall\r\nstandings.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Lupinus\r\n2nd Place: Daisy\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos\x05"
    const MESSAGE_62 = "The results of the seventh\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Lupinus  +10\r\n2nd Place: Daisy  +6\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos  +4\r\n4th Place: Sylvia  +3\r\n5th Place: Lavender  +2\r\n6th Place: Amaryllis  +1\r\n7th Place: Moraea\r\n8th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (unch.): Licorice  40\r\n2nd (unch.): Cosmos  34\r\n2nd (up): Daisy  34\r\n2nd (up): Lupinus  34\r\n5th (unch.): Miltonia  16\r\n6th (unch.): Sylvia  9\r\n7th (down): Moraea  6\r\n8th (unch.): Amaryllis  5\r\n9th (unch.): Lavender  4\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_63 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMoraea\r\n\x81@On Natsuki\r\n\x81@Using Summoning Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nI've never seen her summon\r\nanything, though, so I don't\r\nrightly know just what this\r\nmeans.\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELupinus\r\n\x81@On Maho\r\n\x81@Using Illusion Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLupinus's new machine, Maho,\r\nsure seems more powerful\r\nthan its predecessor, though\r\nyou can't necessarily tell\r\nfor sure from just a single\r\nglance.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\neighth match will be the\r\nday after tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_64 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ESylvia\r\n\x81@On Yotsuba\r\n\x81@Using Spirit Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nSylvia's new machine,\r\nYotsuba, can change into any\r\nof four different forms, in\r\naccordance with whichever\r\nmagic she is using at a\r\ngiven time. It's a good one.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMiltonia\r\n\x81@On Sprite\r\n\x81@Using White Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe uses restorative magic,\r\nso she prefers to race\r\npretty hard, and then heal\r\nherself afterwards.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\neighth match will be\r\ntomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_65 = "The results of the eighth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLicorice made a rapid return\r\nto the field. The big\r\ninterest in this race was\r\nhow she would fare against\r\nLupinus, with her new\r\nmachine. As it turned out,\r\nhowever, not even this new\r\nand improved Lupinus could\r\nstop Licorice. In the middle\r\nof the race, Licorice found\r\nherself caught between\r\nLavender and Amaryllis, who\r\nhad been lapped, and it\r\nlooked as though she was in\r\ntrouble for a while. She\r\nescaped through teleporting\r\nahead in the last turn,\r\nhowever, to take the win,\r\nhandily. With two races left\r\nto go, Licorice may just\r\nhave a lock on the\r\nchampionship title already.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice\r\n2nd Place: Lupinus\r\n3rd Place: Daisy\x05"
    const MESSAGE_66 = "The results of the eighth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice  +10\r\n2nd Place: Lupinus  +6\r\n3rd Place: Daisy  +6\r\n4th Place: Cosmos  +3\r\n5th Place: Sylvia  +2\r\n6th Place: Miltonia  +1\r\n7th Place: Moraea\r\n8th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (unch.): Licorice  50\r\n2nd (unch.): Lupinus  40\r\n3rd (down): Daisy  38\r\n4th (down): Cosmos  37\r\n5th (unch.): Miltonia  17\r\n6th (unch.): Sylvia  11\r\n7th (unch.): Moraea  6\r\n8th (unch.): Amaryllis  5\r\n9th (unch.): Lavender  4\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_67 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELicorice\r\n\x81@On Makoto\r\n\x81@Using Spatial Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLicorice's spatial\r\ninterchange magic, which\r\nenables her to change places\r\nwith anyone else, may well\r\nbe the most powerful magic\r\nof all.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELavender\r\n\x81@On Starlight\r\n\x81@Using Divination\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe always divines who will\r\nwin before a race starts.\r\nRumor has it her predictions\r\nare 100% accurate.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nninth match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_68 = "The results of the ninth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nIt may or may not come as a\r\nsurprise, but Licorice won\r\nthis race too, and by a\r\nmargin of 52 seconds over\r\nsecond place finisher\r\nMiltonia. This victory means\r\nthat Licorice has already\r\nwon the championship,\r\nregardless of the outcome of\r\nthe final race. That doesn't\r\nmean the competition is all\r\nover, though. We hope that\r\nall the competitors will\r\ngive their all in the next\r\nrace, even though the\r\nchampionship has already\r\nbeen decided, and they're\r\nnot likely to feel all that\r\nmotivated, as a result...\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice\r\n2nd Place: Miltonia\r\n3rd Place: Daisy\x05"
    const MESSAGE_69 = "The results of the ninth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice  +10\r\n2nd Place: Miltonia  +6\r\n3rd Place: Daisy  +4\r\n4th Place: Cosmos  +3\r\n5th Place: Sylvia  +2\r\n6th Place: Lupinus  +1\r\n7th Place: Lavender\r\n8th Place: Moraea\r\n9th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (unch.): Licorice  60\r\n2nd (up): Daisy  42\r\n3rd (down): Lupinus  41\r\n4th (unch.): Cosmos  40\r\n5th (unch.): Miltonia  23\r\n6th (unch.): Sylvia  13\r\n7th (unch.): Moraea  6\r\n8th (unch.): Amaryllis  5\r\n9th (unch.): Lavender  4\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_70 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EAmaryllis\r\n\x81@On Sakuya\r\n\x81@Using Flower Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAll her magic does is create\r\nflowers, which really isn't\r\nthat useful in racing...\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELiliac\r\n\x81@On Karin\r\n\x81@Trainee in Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAs a trainee, Lilac has no\r\nmagic yet. Let's hope she\r\neventually makes good.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nfinal match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_71 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMoraea\r\n\x81@On Natsuki\r\n\x81@Using Summoning Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nI've never seen her summon\r\nanything, though, so I don't\r\nrightly know just what this\r\nmeans.\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELupinus\r\n\x81@On Maho\r\n\x81@Using Illusion Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLupinus's new machine, Maho,\r\nsure seems more powerful\r\nthan its predecessor, though\r\nyou can't necessarily tell\r\nfor sure from just a single\r\nglance.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nfinal match will be\r\ntomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_72 = "The results of the final\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThis last race was pretty\r\nlackluster, probably owing\r\nto the fact that Licorice\r\nalready had the championship\r\nall sewn up for this season.\r\nOnly Licorice and Sylvia\r\nmade a real race of it, in\r\nfact. And even though she\r\nwas no match for Licorice,\r\nSylvia still managed to take\r\nsecond place with a two\r\nminute edge over third-place\r\nfinisher Lupinus.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice\r\n2nd Place: Sylvia\r\n3rd Place: Lupinus\x05"
    const MESSAGE_73 = "The results of the final\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice  +10\r\n2nd Place: Sylvia  +6\r\n3rd Place Lupinus  +4\r\n4th Place: Daisy  +3\r\n5th Place: Cosmos  +2\r\n6th Place: Miltonia  +1\r\n7th Place: Lavender\r\n8th Place: Liliac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (unch.): Licorice  70\r\n2nd (unch.): Daisy  45\r\n2nd (up): Lupinus  45\r\n4th (unch.): Cosmos  42\r\n5th (unch.): Miltonia  24\r\n6th (unch.): Sylvia  19\r\n7th (unch.): Moraea  6\r\n8th (unch.): Amaryllis  5\r\n9th (unch.): Lavender  4\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_74 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ESylvia\r\n\x81@On Mayo\r\n\x81@Using Spirit Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nSylvia's new machine, Mayo,\r\nis an upgraded model of her\r\nYotsuba machine. It, too,\r\ncan take on any of four\r\ndifferent forms, in\r\naccordance with whichever \r\nmagic she is using at a\r\ngiven time. It's another\r\ngood one.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMiltonia\r\n\x81@On Sprite\r\n\x81@Using White Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe uses restorative magic,\r\nso she prefers to race\r\npretty hard, and then heal\r\nherself afterwards.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nfirst match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_75 = "The results of the first\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nIt's only the first race of\r\nthe season, but things are\r\noff to a riotous start. If\r\nyou can imagine, Eucomyth,\r\nrunning in her first race\r\never, found herself in a\r\nshowdown against Daisy and\r\nCosmos, the Children of\r\nLight and Darkness\r\nthemselves, who were using\r\nnew models of their Peony\r\nmachines. Licorice, who won\r\nthe previous championship by\r\nan overwhelming margin, was\r\nhandicapped this time around\r\nby a malfunctioning machine.\r\nShe attempted to recover\r\nmidway through the race by\r\nmeans of her spatial\r\ninterchange magic. Eucomyth,\r\nhowever, avoided it, amazing\r\nas that sounds, and coasted\r\nto a win. Licorice ended up\r\ncoming in sixth.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Eucomyth\r\n2nd Place: Daisy\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos\x05"
    const MESSAGE_76 = "The results of the first\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Eucomyth  +10\r\n2nd Place: Daisy  +6\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos  +4\r\n4th Place: Lupinus  +3\r\n5th Place: Sylvia  +2\r\n6th Place: Licorice  +1\r\n7th Place: Miltonia\r\n8th Place: Lavender\r\n9th Place: Moraea\r\n10th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st: Eucomyth  10\r\n2nd: Daisy  6\r\n3rd: Cosmos  4\r\n4th: Lupinus  3\r\n5th: Sylvia  2\r\n6th: Licorice  1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_77 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EDaisy\r\n\x81@On Peony\r\n\x81@Using Light Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nCan anyone catch her when\r\nshe uses her Shining Wing\r\nspell?\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ECosmos\r\n\x81@On Peony\r\n\x81@Using Darkness Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nCosmos, Daisy's twin sister,\r\nhas magic opposite but\r\nalmost as powerful in her\r\nDark Wing spell.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nsecond match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_78 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EEucomyth\r\n\x81@On Kyoko\r\n\x81@Using Temporal Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe may be new to the game,\r\nbut she's got powerful\r\nmagic. How do you stop\r\nsomeone who can stop time\r\nitself?\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELiliac\r\n\x81@On Karin\r\n\x81@Trainee in Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAs a trainee, Lilac has no\r\nmagic yet. Let's hope she\r\neventually makes good.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nsecond match will be\r\ntomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_79 = "The results of the second\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLicorice, who struggled in\r\nthe last race with machine\r\ntroubles, was in top form\r\nthis time around. In the\r\nfinal lap, however, Eucomyth\r\napparently used her ultimate\r\nmagic, personal time, and\r\ntook first place while all\r\nthe rest of us were frozen\r\nin time. That time stop\r\naffected everyone, myself\r\nincluded, which means that\r\neven I don't rightly know\r\njust what happened. The\r\npoint is, Eucomyth suddenly\r\npopped in front of Licorice,\r\nand was thus first across\r\nthe line.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Eucomyth\r\n2nd Place: Licorice\r\n3rd Place: Daisy\x05"
    const MESSAGE_80 = "The results of the second\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Eucomyth  +10\r\n2nd Place: Licorice  +6\r\n3rd Place: Daisy  +4\r\n4th Place: Cosmos  +3\r\n5th Place: Lupinus  +2\r\n6th Place: Miltonia  +1\r\n7th Place: Lavender\r\n8th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (unch.): Eucomyth  20\r\n2nd (unch.): Daisy  10\r\n3rd (unch.): Cosmos  7\r\n3rd (up): Licorice  7\r\n5th (down): Lupinus  5\r\n6th (down): Sylvia  2\r\n7th (up): Miltonia  1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_81 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ESylvia\r\n\x81@On Mayo\r\n\x81@Using Spirit Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nSylvia's new machine, Mayo,\r\nis an upgraded model of her\r\nYotsuba machine. It, too,\r\ncan take on any of four\r\ndifferent forms, in\r\naccordance with whichever \r\nmagic she is using at a\r\ngiven time. It's another\r\ngood one.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMiltonia\r\n\x81@On Sprite\r\n\x81@Using White Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe uses restorative magic,\r\nso she prefers to race\r\npretty hard, and then heal\r\nherself afterwards.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nthird match will be\r\ntomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_82 = "The results of the third\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nEucomyth must still have\r\nbeen feeling the\r\naftereffects of using her\r\nultimate temporal magic in\r\nthe last race. Whatever the\r\nreason, she was unable to\r\ndodge the Blue Dragon that\r\nMoraea summoned this time,\r\nand it blew her off the\r\ntrack. Moraea was herself\r\ncaught up in the collateral\r\neffects, however, which\r\nwiped her out as well, thus\r\nleaving the field clear for\r\nLicorice. Lupinus fought\r\nback with all she had, but\r\nto no avail, as Licorice\r\nsailed to her first victory\r\nof the season.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice\r\n2nd Place: Lupinus\r\n3rd Place: Daisy\x05"
    const MESSAGE_83 = "The results of the third\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice  +10\r\n2nd Place: Lupinus  +6\r\n3rd Place: Daisy  +4\r\n4th Place: Cosmos  +3\r\n5th Place: Miltonia  +2\r\n6th Place: Sylvia  +1\r\n7th Place: Lavender\r\n8th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (unch.): Eucomyth  20\r\n2nd (up): Licorice  17\r\n3rd (down): Daisy  14\r\n4th (up): Lupinus  11\r\n5th (down): Cosmos  10\r\n6th (unch.): Sylvia  3\r\n6th (up): Miltonia  3\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_84 = "The results of the fourth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nEven before this race\r\nstarted, there already was a\r\nmajor upset in the works.\r\nLavender's divination\r\nforetold that she would\r\ncollide with Eucomyth in the\r\nrace, taking them both out.\r\nEucomyth paid attention to\r\nthe warning, and stayed out\r\nof the race, as did\r\nLavender, possibly out of\r\nrespect for Eucomyth's\r\ndecision. Licorice was also\r\nout of today's race. The\r\nword is she had an upset\r\nstomach.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Daisy\r\n2nd Place: Cosmos\r\n3rd Place: Miltonia\x05"
    const MESSAGE_85 = "The results of the third\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Daisy  +10\r\n2nd Place: Cosmos  +6\r\n3rd Place: Miltonia  +4\r\n4th Place: Lupinus  +3\r\n5th Place: Sylvia  +2\r\n6th Place: Moraea  +1\r\n7th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (up): Daisy  24\r\n2nd (down): Eucomyth  20\r\n3rd (down): Licorice  17\r\n4th (up): Cosmos  16\r\n5th (down): Lupinus  14\r\n6th (unch.): Miltonia  7\r\n7th (down): Sylvia  5\r\n8th (up): Moraea  1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_86 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EEucomyth\r\n\x81@On Kyoko\r\n\x81@Using Temporal Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe may be new to the game,\r\nbut she's got powerful\r\nmagic. How do you stop\r\nsomeone who can stop time\r\nitself?\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELiliac\r\n\x81@On Karin\r\n\x81@Trainee in Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAs a trainee, Lilac has no\r\nmagic yet. Let's hope she\r\neventually makes good.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nfifth match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_87 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMoraea\r\n\x81@On Natsuki\r\n\x81@Using Summoning Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nI've never seen her summon\r\nanything, though, so I don't\r\nrightly know just what this\r\nmeans.\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELupinus\r\n\x81@On Maho\r\n\x81@Using Illusion Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLupinus's new machine, Maho,\r\nsure seems more powerful\r\nthan its predecessor, though\r\nyou can't necessarily tell\r\nfor sure from just a single\r\nglance.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nfifth match will be\r\ntomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_88 = "The results of the fifth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThis race had the first\r\nshowdown between Eucomyth\r\nand  Licorice in three runs.\r\nEucomyth ran the field at\r\nher own pace, and Licorice\r\ncouldn't get past her. She\r\nappeared to hesitate to use\r\nher spatial interchange\r\nmagic, however, perhaps out\r\nof fear that Eucomyth might\r\ndodge it altogether, as she\r\ndid the last time they met.\r\nInstead, she burned her\r\nmagic power in teleporting,\r\nbut it wasn't quite good\r\nenough. Licorice came in\r\nsecond behind Eucomyth, who\r\nnow once again holds first\r\nplace in the overall\r\nstandings.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Eucomyth\r\n2nd Place: Licorice\r\n3rd Place: Lupinus\x05"
    const MESSAGE_89 = "The results of the fifth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Eucomyth  +10\r\n2nd Place: Licorice  +6\r\n3rd Place: Lupinus  +4\r\n4th Place: Daisy  +3\r\n5th Place: Cosmos  +2\r\n6th Place: Miltonia  +1\r\n7th Place: Sylvia\r\n8th Place: Moraea\r\n9th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (up): Eucomyth  30\r\n2nd (down): Daisy  27\r\n3rd (unch.): Licorice  23\r\n4th (unch.): Cosmos  18\r\n5th (unch.): Lupinus  18\r\n6th (unch.): Miltonia  8\r\n7th (unch.): Sylvia  5\r\n8th (unch.): Moraea  1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_90 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ESylvia\r\n\x81@On Mayo\r\n\x81@Using Spirit Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nSylvia's new machine, Mayo,\r\nis an upgraded model of her\r\nYotsuba machine. It, too,\r\ncan take on any of four\r\ndifferent forms, in\r\naccordance with whichever \r\nmagic she is using at a\r\ngiven time. It's another\r\ngood one.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMiltonia\r\n\x81@On Sprite\r\n\x81@Using White Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe uses restorative magic,\r\nso she prefers to race\r\npretty hard, and then heal\r\nherself afterwards.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nsixth match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_91 = "The results of the sixth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLavender's divination\r\nforetold that she and Cosmos\r\nwould collide during today's\r\nrace, taking them both out.\r\nThere was no way that Cosmos\r\nwould simply take such news\r\nlying down, however. And\r\nwouldn't you know it,\r\nLavender was right. Just\r\nbefore being taken out,\r\nthough, Cosmos transferred\r\nall of her remaining magic\r\npower to Daisy, thus giving\r\nher what she needed to win\r\nthe race, by putting all of\r\nthe magic power she'd been\r\ngiven into her Shining Wing\r\nthroughout all the remaining\r\nlaps.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Daisy\r\n2nd Place: Eucomyth\r\n3rd Place: Licorice\x05"
    const MESSAGE_92 = "The results of the sixth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Daisy  +10\r\n2nd Place: Eucomyth  +6\r\n3rd Place: Licorice  +4\r\n4th Place: Lupinus  +3\r\n5th Place: Sylvia  +2\r\n6th Place: Miltonia  +1\r\n7th Place: Moraea\r\n8th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (up): Daisy  37\r\n2nd (down): Eucomyth  36\r\n3rd (unch.): Licorice  27\r\n4th (up): Lupinus  21\r\n5th (down): Cosmos  18\r\n6th (unch.): Miltonia  9\r\n7th (unch.): Sylvia  7\r\n8th (unch.): Moraea  1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_93 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EEucomyth\r\n\x81@On Kyoko\r\n\x81@Using Temporal Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe may be new to the game,\r\nbut she's got powerful\r\nmagic. How do you stop\r\nsomeone who can stop time\r\nitself?\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELiliac\r\n\x81@On Karin\r\n\x81@Trainee in Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAs a trainee, Lilac has no\r\nmagic yet. Let's hope she\r\neventually makes good.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nseventh match will be\r\ntomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_94 = "The results of the seventh\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAs before, this race came\r\ndown to Eucomyth and\r\nLicorice, the latter using\r\nher teleport power with\r\ntiming so exquisite that it\r\nseemed certain that she\r\nwould pass up Eucomyth. Only\r\nthing was, Eucomyth used\r\nforesight with the exact\r\nsame timing to know what\r\nLicorice was going to do\r\nbefore she did it, thus\r\nblocking her completely.\r\nBoth Daisy and Cosmos were\r\nout of today's race, the\r\nlatter because she used up\r\nan excessive amount of magic\r\npower on her sister in the\r\nprevious race.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Eucomyth\r\n2nd Place: Licorice\r\n3rd Place: Lupinus\x05"
    const MESSAGE_95 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMoraea\r\n\x81@On Natsuki\r\n\x81@Using Summoning Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nI've never seen her summon\r\nanything, though, so I don't\r\nrightly know just what this\r\nmeans.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELupinus\r\n\x81@On Misuzu\r\n\x81@Using Illusion Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAll she does is illusion, so\r\nif you figure that out,\r\nshe's totally powerless.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\n8th match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_96 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMoraea\r\n\x81@On Natsuki\r\n\x81@Using Summoning Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nI've never seen her summon\r\nanything, though, so I don't\r\nrightly know just what this\r\nmeans.\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELupinus\r\n\x81@On Maho\r\n\x81@Using Illusion Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nLupinus's new machine, Maho,\r\nsure seems more powerful\r\nthan its predecessor, though\r\nyou can't necessarily tell\r\nfor sure from just a single\r\nglance.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\neighth match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_97 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ESylvia\r\n\x81@On Mayo\r\n\x81@Using Spirit Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nSylvia's new machine, Mayo,\r\nis an upgraded model of her\r\nYotsuba machine. It, too,\r\ncan take on any of four\r\ndifferent forms, in\r\naccordance with whichever \r\nmagic she is using at a\r\ngiven time. It's another\r\ngood one.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EMiltonia\r\n\x81@On Sprite\r\n\x81@Using White Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe uses restorative magic,\r\nso she prefers to race\r\npretty hard, and then heal\r\nherself afterwards.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\neighth match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_98 = "The results of the eighth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nSylvia plowed smack into a\r\nwall toward the end of the\r\nrace, wiping herself out in\r\nspectacular fashion. Pieces\r\nof her machine Yotsuba flew\r\neverywhere, with several of\r\nthem connecting with\r\nEucomyth, who was right\r\nbehind her at the time.\r\nEucomyth's machine Kyoko\r\nstarted to fail on her, such\r\nthat she ended up coming in\r\nsecond, having been passed\r\nup by Licorice. Eucomyth is\r\nstill tops in the overall\r\nrankings, however, with a\r\nnine-point lead over\r\nLicorice. Can Licorice make\r\nup the deficit in the two\r\nraces remaining this season?\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice\r\n2nd Place: Eucomyth\r\n3rd Place: Daisy\x05"
    const MESSAGE_99 = "The results of the eighth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice  +10\r\n2nd Place: Eucomyth  +6\r\n3rd Place: Daisy  +4\r\n4th Place: Cosmos  +3\r\n5th Place: Lupinus  +2\r\n6th Place: Miltonia  +1\r\n7th Place: Moraea\r\n8th Place: Lavender\r\n9th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (unch.): Eucomyth  52\r\n2nd (up): Licorice  43\r\n3rd (down): Daisy  41\r\n4th (unch.): Lupinus  27\r\n5th (unch.): Cosmos  21\r\n6th (unch.): Miltonia  13\r\n7th (unch.): Sylvia  8\r\n8th (unch.): Moraea 2\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_100 = "The results of the ninth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAs Lupinus and Miltonia were\r\nfighting it out for fifth\r\nplace, they found themselves\r\nlapped by Eucomyth. The\r\nsheer intensity of their\r\nbattle, however, snagged\r\nEucomyth, giving her no way\r\nto get safely past. And just\r\nthen, Licorice came up from\r\nbehind. In desperation,\r\nEucomyth tried using her\r\nultimate personal time\r\nmagic, leaving herself with\r\nno concentration or defense,\r\nwhen ripples from the magic\r\nbeing thrown off by Lupinus\r\nand Miltonia ahead of her\r\ncaused her to lose her\r\nbalance and pitch forward,\r\ntaking both of them out of\r\nthe race with her. As a\r\nconsequence, only one point\r\nnow separates first and\r\nsecond place in the overall\r\nrankings.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice\r\n2nd Place: Daisy\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos\x05"
    const MESSAGE_101 = "The results of the ninth\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice  +10\r\n2nd Place: Daisy  +6\r\n3rd Place: Cosmos  +4\r\n4th Place: Moraea  +3\r\n5th Place: Sylvia  +2\r\n6th Place: Lavender  +1\r\n7th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (up): Licorice  53\r\n2nd (down): Eucomyth  52\r\n3rd (unch.): Daisy  47\r\n4th (unch.): Lupinus  27\r\n5th (unch.): Cosmos  25\r\n6th (unch.): Miltonia  13\r\n7th (unch.): Sylvia  10\r\n8th (unch.): Moraea  5\r\n9th (up): Lavender  1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_102 = "Racers in the F-3.14 MGP\r\nare as follows:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81EEucomyth\r\n\x81@On Kyoko\r\n\x81@Using Temporal Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nShe may be new to the game,\r\nbut she's got powerful\r\nmagic. How do you stop\r\nsomeone who can stop time\r\nitself?\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\x81|\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81ELiliac\r\n\x81@On Karin\r\n\x81@Trainee in Magic\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAs a trainee, Lilac has no\r\nmagic yet. Let's hope she\r\neventually makes good.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nThat's all for today. The\r\nfinal match will be the day\r\nafter tomorrow.\x05"
    const MESSAGE_103 = "The results of the final\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nEven if Daisy had managed to\r\nwin this race, she could not\r\nhave won the championship if\r\neither Eucomyth or Licorice\r\ncame in second. Thus, this\r\nfinal race, as with so many\r\nothers this season, came\r\ndown to a contest between\r\nEucomyth and Licorice. And\r\nEucomyth ran the field at\r\nher own pace, up until the\r\nfinal stretch, whereupon\r\nLicorice used her spatial\r\ninversion magic. Eucomyth,\r\nwho had been expecting that\r\nmove with ease. Licorice,\r\nhowever, wasted no time in\r\ndoing it again, something\r\nthat Eucomyth apparently\r\nhadn't expected, because she\r\ngot nailed by it, a direct\r\nhit, with the net result\r\nbeing that Licorice won the\r\nrace, and her second\r\nchampionship title in a row.\r\nOur go congratulations go\r\nout to her.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nFor now, we have the top\r\nthree racers. We'll post the\r\nfull results tomorrow.\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nRace Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice\r\n2nd Place: Eucomyth\r\n3rd Place: Daisy\x05"
    const MESSAGE_104 = "The results of the final\r\nF-3.14 MGP Race are:\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nYesterday's Race Results:\r\n1st Place: Licorice  +10\r\n2nd Place: Eucomyth  +6\r\n3rd Place: Daisy  +4\r\n4th Place: Cosmos  +3\r\n5th Place: Miltonia  +2\r\n6th Place: Lupinus  +1\r\n7th Place: Moraea\r\n8th Place: Lilac\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nPoint Standings:\r\n1st (unch.): Licorice  63\r\n2nd (unch.): Eucomyth  58\r\n3rd (unch.): Daisy  51\r\n4th (unch.): Lupinus  28\r\n4th (up): Cosmos  28\r\n6th (unch.): Miltonia  15\r\n7th (unch.): Sylvia  10\r\n8th (unch.): Moraea  5\r\n9th (unch.): Lavender  1\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\n\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\x81@\r\nAnd there you have it.\x05"
